Description: Trigger error if LBSTRESU is not null and LBSTNRC is not expressed using the units in LBSTRESU

Error Message: LBSTNRHI is not expressed using the units in LBSTRESU
Description: Trigger error if LBSTNRHI is not expressed using the units in LBSTRESU

Error Message: COVALn is present in dataset when no comments are greater than 200 characters
Description: Trigger error when there are no comments greater than 200 characters and COVALn is present

Error Message: Comments are not unsolicited, free-text and voluntary
Description: Trigger error when comments are not unsolicited, free-text and voluntary

Error Message: SREL does not describe relationship of associated person to device identified in RDEVID when RDEVID ^= null
Description: Trigger error when RDEVID ^= null and SREL does not describe relationship of associated person to device identified in RDEVID

Error Message: SREL does not describe the relationship of associated person to study subject or pool when RSUBJID is not null
Description: Trigger error when RSUBJID ^= null and SREL does not describe the relationship of associated person to study subject or pool

Error Message: Relationship described is to a study (but not to individua study subject) and RSUBJID is not null
Description: Trigger error if relationship described is to a study (but not to individual study subject) and RSUBJID is not null

Error Message: RSUBJID is not in POOLDEF.POOLID
Description: Trigger error if relationship described is to a pool and RSUBJID is not in POOLDEF.POOLID

Error Message: EXTRT is not a protocol-specified treatment
Description: Trigger error if EXTRT is not the protocol-specified treatment

Error Message: EXDOSU is not expressed using protocol-specific units
Description: Trigger error if EXDOSU not expressed in protocol-specified units

Error Message: SBSTRAIN is present in DM dataset.
Description: Verify variable SBSTRAIN does not exist in DM dataset

Error Message: STRAIN is present in DM dataset.
Description: Verify variable STRAIN does not exist in DM dataset

Error Message: SPECIES is present in DM dataset.
Description: Verify variable SPECIES does not exist in DM dataset

Error Message: TSVCDREF is null when TSVCDVER is populated
Description: Trigger error when TSVCDVER is populated and TSVCDREF is null

Error Message: TSVALNF is not null when TSVAL is populated
Description: Trigger error when TSVAL is populated and TSVALNF is also populated.

Error Message: TSVALNF is null when TSVAL is null.
Description: Trigger error when TSVAL is null and TSVALNF is null

Error Message: IETESTCD is not unique
Description: Trigger error when IETESTCD is not unique within dataset

Error Message: IETESTCD is not unique within TIVERS
Description: Trigger error when TIVERS is present and IETESTCD is not unique within TIVERS

Error Message: RSUBJID is not in DM.USUBJID.
Description: Raise an error when RSUBJID in not in DM.USUBJID

Error Message: CMDECOD must be populated when CMTRT is populated
Description: Raise an error when CMTRT is populated, CMDECOD is empty

Error Message: ARM cannot be equal to 'Screen Failure', 'Not Assigned', 'Unplanned Treatment' or 'Not Treated'.
Description: Raise an error when ARM is 'Screen Failure', 'Not Assigned', 'Unplanned Treatment', 'Not Treated'

Error Message: Record is derived in a data collection tool and RSDRVFL is not equal to "Y"
Description: Raise an error when record is derived in a data collection tool and RSDRVFL is not equal to "Y"

Error Message: SMSTDTC is null.
Description: Raise an error when SMSTDTC is null.

Error Message: Primary analysis used but --BODSYS and --SOC are not equal
Description: Raise an error if primary SOC is used for analysis and -BODSYS is not equal to -SOC

Error Message: Value for --VAMTU is populated, when --TRTV is NULL.
Description: Raise an error when --TRTV is null, --VAMTU is not null

Error Message: EXVAMTU is present when EC domain exists.
Description: When EC exists, EXVAMTU should not be used.

Error Message: Value for --VAMT is populated, when --TRTV is NULL.
Description: Raise an error when --TRTV is empty, --VAMT is not empty

Error Message: PESTRESC value is not missing when PEORRES value is missing
Description: Verify that PESTRESC is null when PEORRES is null

Error Message: '--LAT is present when --LOC is not present.
Description: Raise an error when --LOC is not present and --LAT is present.

Error Message: TRLAT is present.
Description: Raise an error when TRLAT is present.

Error Message: TRDIR is present.
Description: Raise an error when TRDIR is present.

Error Message: TRPORTOT is present.
Description: Raise an error when TRPORTOT is present.

Error Message: RPATHCD is present.
Description: Raise an error when RPATHCD is present.

Error Message: '--BEATNO is present.
Description: Raise an error when --BEATNO is present.

Error Message: '--EVALID is present.  --EVALID must not be used to model QRS data.
Description: '--EVALID must not be used to model QRS data.   This includes the 'QS' and 'FT' domains as well as the 'RS' domain when the record pertains to a Clinical Classification Use Case). This rule has been fully executed for the QS and FT domains only.

Error Message: '--EVAL is present.  --EVAL must not be used to model QRS data.
Description: '--EVAL must not be used to model QRS data.   This includes the 'QS' and 'FT' domains as well as the 'RS' domain when the record pertains to a Clinical Classification Use Case). This rule has been fully executed for the QS and FT domains only.

Error Message: LBORNRLO is not expressed using the units in LBORRESU
Description: LBORNRLO is expressed using the units in LBORRESU

Error Message: EXTRT is PLACEBO, but EXDOSE is not equal to 0.
Description: When EXTRT is PLACEBO, EXDOSE must equal 0

Error Message: TRLOC is present when TRLOC is not included in the TR domain.
Description: Raise an error when TRLOC is present.

Error Message: SESTDTC is required.
Description: Raise an error when SESTDTC is null.

Error Message: ECDOSE is less than or equal to 0
Description: Verify the value for ECDOSE is less than 0
